{"tid":2172301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七一刺警案 被告再次申請保釋被拒 放棄覆核保釋權利 還柙至11月再訊","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T16:33:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2bc04134ab1363cda21a5fc1b799687a1ff5aed","tid":2172301,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/7-1-%E5%88%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E7%BA%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E6%AA%A2%E7%8D%B2%E6%8C%87%E7%B4%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-1-%25E5%2588%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%25BA%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25B4%258B%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=f5771753\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F7-1-%25E5%2588%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%25BA%258C%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25B4%258B%2F&h=b6e84d8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/7-1-%E5%88%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%94%B3%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E7%BA%8C%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E6%AA%A2%E7%8D%B2%E6%8C%87%E7%B4%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n本年 7 月 1 日《港區國安法》生效後第一天，大批市民在港島各處聚集。一名警員下午在維園外制服示威者期間被短刀刺中，左肩流血受傷。被指涉案的 24 歲男子當晚在機場被捕，被控一項有意圖而傷人罪；而當時分別推開該警員的 17 歲男學生及正被該警員制服的 19 歲男學生則被控阻差辦公罪。案件今（24 日）在東區裁判法院再提堂。控方稱上次提堂後，警方在觀塘區檢獲一個背囊，在內的兩把短刀其中一把有 24 歲被告的指紋。控方申請押後案件至 11 月 10 日再提堂，以作進一步調查及索取法律意見獲批。24 歲被告今提出以合共 40 萬元申請保釋被拒，另兩人則獲准以原有條件擔保。"},{"pid":"c4f51f0e890c6425dbc6574c3ffa383b8e9dc10c","tid":2172301,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>泛民最後嘅翻身機會已經喺面前！</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2172259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2172259</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4841de2f7b3ffef74601938824499348d4f2dfd","tid":2172301,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F8573&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbl8MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=1b31a11c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/8573</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n#20200701銅鑼灣 #提堂<br />\n<br />\n黃 (24)🛑已還押逾1個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪：有意圖而傷人<br />\n<br />\n案情：於2020年7月1日在皇仁書院外意圖使警員25116身體受嚴重傷害，並非法及惡意傷害警員25116。<br />\n<br />\n控方申請押後以供警方調查及索取法律意見<br />\n<br />\n被告申請保釋被拒❌<br />\n辯方放棄8日覆核權利<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至11月10日1430東區裁判法院第一庭再訊，期間被告需繼續還押。"},{"pid":"b9595db194d96e54e58d1e2bae6bb928c799f5f1","tid":2172301,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"差少少走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686f01ecc2ca9aa693d6a8a86285e6c726243885","tid":2172301,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9595db194d96e54e58d1e2bae6bb928c799f5f1","tid":2172301,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"差少少走得甩<img src=\"/asset